long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Prodsee lets you share share documents, files, images or links with your team and lets you tag items so it's always easy for anyone to find. 

Tag content that you share so that anyone across your company can find documents and you'll never lose work again. 

With the Prodsee extension you can even automatically take a full page screenshot to share with your team. 

To get started, just log in or sign up for a free Prodsee account.
